        <Parent_String>Gothic scripts [300195226], Latin and Greek alphabet scripts [300208614], scripts by form [300201815], scripts (writing) [300200824], script and type forms [300201263], information form components [300201262], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
